snippet.title: DASHBALL - Official Trailer for Playstation 4
snippet.description:
Welcome to DASHBALL!
Gather your friends and get ready for some intense and fun action in splitscreen multiplayer for up to 4 players. 
You join the "old batch" and will have to travel the world to show everyone that you and your squad are the ultimate dashball champions.

The game is now out on Playstation 4 in several regions. If you cannot find it yet, kindly let us know and we will give you an update.

Licensed song: Cadillac Money 2 through AudioNetwork.com

You got any feedback for the game or got any questions? Comment here or send us a message. We would really appreciate that!
